I think he needs to have a talk with Trump. permalink award report block reply Trooph-Hurts 9 points 57 minutes ago Having worked in MFG for 45 years I can tell you H1B workers have ZERO to offer where we want MFG to go in America…. India and China are the most backwards places of low skill workers you can ever imagine….. they get the job done only through brute force…… they are dangerous, unsafe unskilled! ,,,,, the only thing they are is CHEAP permalink award report block reply RedStoneDeepState 1 points 9 minutes ago Yep. I have worked with skilled people in manufacturing who were immigrants... They are Israeli, Japanese, Korean, German or Soviet-Sphere.
